VINCULOS.OUTRAS-INFORMACOES:
He is Professor at the Computer Science Center of the Federal University of Pernambuco, Associate Researcher to the Brazilian Council for Scientific and Technological Development. He has expertise in the areas of:
* Design and deployment of (e|m|t|u)-learning environments;
* Qualitative research of human behavior;
* Open source & service-oriented learning technology;
* Design Thinking, Design Research, Value co-creation, Customer experience;
* Enterprise information solutions user experience.

